  "title": "Service Engineer | $3,500 + AWS + VB",
  "description": "<p><strong>Service Engineer</strong> <em>(for electronics & semiconductor industries)</em><br />Location: Kallang<br />Working hours: 9am - 5.30pm<br /><br /><strong>Job Description & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provides on-site technical support, installation, troubleshooting and maintenance services for machines (Laser Processing Machines, PCB Drilling Machines etc.)</li><li>Deliver high quality technical support to our customers</li><li>Ensure customer satisfaction through timely and effective service</li><li>Prepare reports, ‘Contact and Consult’ at work</li><li>Stay updated with new technology and industry trend to maintain expertise and provide proactive support including thinking flexibly</li><li>Any other technical or engineering related duties assigned by Management</li></ul><p><strong>Required Skills and Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Mechanical Engineering, Electrical Engineering or a related field</li><li>At least 3 years of experience as a service engineer, service technician or similar role in technical support and maintenance</li><li>Strong technical skills and knowledge of mechanical, or electronic systems and components</li><li>Knowledge of safety protocols and standards for working with machinery and equipment</li><li>Excellent problem-solving and diagnostic abilities, with the ability to analyse and resolve technical issues efficiently</li><li>Customer-focused attitude with strong communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team</li><li>Possess good interaction skills and able to explain things logically</li><li>Willingness to work overtime and during weekends if necessary</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested parties, please email to <em><strong>kyo@temp-team.com.sg</strong></em><br />Karin Yong<br />Registration: R22109239<br />EA Licence: 01C3135</p><p></p>",
